  <excerpt>Maybe not the best on the market but definitely one that works for me and at the end of the day: free.</excerpt>
  <content>&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;I was.  Two months ago.  Not any more.  I’m not the type that buys on impulse – at least I think I’m not – so it took plenty of searching the web, reading articles, watching YouTube videos, and asking question to family/friends and vendors before I took the plunge.  And so I settled for what I thought was the best value: HTC Radar WP7 with a T-Mobile contract.  Here is a picture of what my phone looks like:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;&lt;a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130724015551/http://tensignals.com/abelgaxiola/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Radar1.jpg" style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(25, 130, 209);"&gt;&lt;img title="Radar" border="0" alt="Radar" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20130724015551im_/http://tensignals.com/abelgaxiola/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Radar_thumb1.jpg" width="222" height="167" style="margin-top: 0.4em; max-width: 97.5%; background-image: none; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; padding-top: 0px;" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;Now after almost two months of owning this phone I couldn’t be happier for my decision.  I paid $160.00 out of pocket and received $100.00 trade for my old phone.  In addition I received a $50.00 rebate from T-Mobile and a $25.00 gift certificate from Windows to be used on the WP7 marketplace.  So, if my math is correct I came out ahead.  Way ahead.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;I know that owning a WP7 is not the cool thing in this day and age but let me tell you something:  WP7 is a very cool platform and the HTC Radar rocks!  If you don’t believe me read the following reviews; and do watch the following video (first link below):&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;&lt;a title="http://www.win7gear.com/wp7-news/faster-than-windows-phone-challenge-at-ces-2012-recap/" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130724015551/http://www.win7gear.com/wp7-news/faster-than-windows-phone-challenge-at-ces-2012-recap/" style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(25, 130, 209);"&gt;faster-than-windows-phone-challenge-at-ces-2012-recap&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;&lt;a title="http://www.zdnet.com/blog/cell-phones/seven-reasons-i-chose-the-htc-radar-4g-over-the-nokia-lumia-710/7174" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130724015551/http://www.zdnet.com/blog/cell-phones/seven-reasons-i-chose-the-htc-radar-4g-over-the-nokia-lumia-710/7174" style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(25, 130, 209);"&gt;seven-reasons-i-chose-the-htc-radar-4g-over-the-nokia-lumia-710/7174&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;&lt;a title="http://www.phonearena.com/news/Windows-Phone-at-the-top-of-the-charts-at-Amazon_id25094" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130724015551/http://www.phonearena.com/news/Windows-Phone-at-the-top-of-the-charts-at-Amazon_id25094" style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(25, 130, 209);"&gt;Windows-Phone-at-the-top-of-the-charts-at-Amazon&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;&lt;a title="http://www.wingadgetnews.com/top-reasons-windows-phone/" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130724015551/http://www.wingadgetnews.com/top-reasons-windows-phone/" style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(25, 130, 209);"&gt;top-reasons-windows-phone&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;&lt;a title="http://www.zdnet.com/blog/cell-phones/torn-between-two-smartphonesfeeling-like-a-fool/7264?tag=mantle_skin;content" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130724015551/http://www.zdnet.com/blog/cell-phones/torn-between-two-smartphonesfeeling-like-a-fool/7264?tag=mantle_skin;content" style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(25, 130, 209);"&gt;torn-between-two-smartphonesfeeling-like-a-fool&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;So, if you’re in the same boat I was a couple of months ago take my advice: get a WP7.  You’ll be happy you did.  Or, you can do what I did: spend a couple of weeks researching your options.  Buy what you think is the best value, and share your thoughts two months later.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
